SubjectCanada-Sinai Multinational Force and Observers ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between the Government of Canada and the Multinational Force and Observers constituting an Agreement further Amending the AGREEMENT ON THE PARTICIPATION OF CANADA IN THE SINAI MULTINATIONAL FORCE AND OBSERVERS.
